  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Effect of Non Invasive Ventilation on end-expiratory lung volumes determined by electrical
      impedance tomography
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Prospective clinical study in ICU with patients requiring non invasive ventilation (NIV)
      comparing lung volumes determined by electrical impedance tomography before, during and
      after NIV.

      Duration of NIV is 30 minutes.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
